# Routine Execution

Follow the **Routine execution** section in [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md):

- **Session start:** From repo root, run `npm run test && npm run lint` before writing new code (after `npm install` if needed).
- **Before push:** Run `npm run test && npm run lint` again from repo root.

Use the Session kickoff template and the directory-structure mapping in AGENTS.md when scoping tasks and verification.
